      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CINDY'S PATCH (2) ran a good time (18.29) winning a Mix 2/3 two back at this track but missed the frame latest finishing fourth at this track. With a good start should be able to take advantage of the low draw. Can make amends this time. VALENTINO BEACH (3) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (18.62) at this track behind CINDY'S PATCH in a Mix 2/3. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Good beginner aided by a nice draw. Can feature again. TORVI TARO (1) missed the frame latest when seventh at this track (23.72) but scored four back at this track (23.04). Has good early burn and is suited drawn on the inside. Can figure in the finish. NANGAR ARCHIE (8) was out of placings last time (20.34) at Grafton in a NG, finishing sixth and beaten 8 lengths. Has seven wins already from this draw.",
